Story: "Accounts"
 
  As an admin
  I want to create accounts
  So I can account money

  Scenario: Create a new account

    Given a new VISA account
    And a number of existing accounts

    When I save the account

    Then the account should be valid
    And there should be 1 more account


  Scenario: Spending money from an account
    Given an account called 'My Wallet' with an opening balance of 100.00

    When 35.00 is spent on lunch
    And 60.00 is spent on fuel

    Then the account should have a balance of 5.00




